MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1662. Koenig v. Vrable II, Inc.

Cuyahoga App. No. 95252. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

*1610It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
